# SL1C3D-L4BS · Stack & brand

This project is the **SL1C3D-L4BS** dotfiles and workstation config. Single source of truth via [chezmoi](https://www.chezmoi.io); one apply, one stack, one brand.

## Stack

- **OS:** Arch Linux
- **WM:** Hyprland (colors, binds, autostart, programs in `~/.config/hypr/`). User overrides: `custom.conf` (sourced last). Lock: hyprlock (Super+L); idle: hypridle. Keybind help: Super+/ runs `~/.config/hypr/scripts/keybinds.sh` (Fuzzel). Window overview: Super+A runs `~/.config/hypr/scripts/overview.sh` (Fuzzel list → focus).
- **Bar:** Quickshell (QML), `~/.config/quickshell/`
- **Terminal:** Ghostty, theme `sl1c3d-l4bs`, JetBrains Mono Nerd Font
- **Prompt:** Starship, `~/.config/starship.toml`, palette `brand`
- **Launcher:** Fuzzel | **FM:** Yazi | **Notifications:** Mako
- **Editor (terminal):** NvChad (custom lua, base46 brand)
- **Multiplexer:** Zellij, theme `brand`
- **Dotfiles:** chezmoi, source `~/.local/share/chezmoi`; alias `cm`

Elite CLI: Atuin, Fastfetch, Zoxide, eza/bat/fd/ripgrep, Delta (git), btop, Lazygit. Install scripts in `~/.config/SL1C3D-L4BS/system-config/`.

