## Conventions

- Config lives under `~/.config/`; dotfiles applied via `chezmoi apply`.
- No redundant READMEs; single root README. Scripts only where needed (system-config installers).
- Validation: `~/scripts/validate-configs.sh` (Yazi, Fuzzel, Mako, Hypr — all 9 sourced files).
- When editing Hypr/QML/shell/config, preserve existing style and brand colors.
